---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header';
import Footer from '../components/Footer';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - OrdersLift" description="Read OrdersLift's terms of service. Understand your rights and obligations when using our AI-powered restaurant website services.">
  <Header client:load />
  
  <main class="pt-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
        
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: January 2024</p>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              By accessing and using OrdersLift's AI-powered restaurant website services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. 
              If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our services.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. Service Description</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              OrdersLift provides AI-powered website solutions for restaurants, including:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
              <li>AI menu chatbot with voice and text capabilities</li>
              <li>Sales insights dashboard and analytics</li>
              <li>Direct delivery integration</li>
              <li>Customer engagement automation</li>
              <li>Order processing and management</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. Restaurant Responsibilities</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">As a restaurant using our services, you agree to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
              <li>Provide accurate and up-to-date menu information</li>
              <li>Maintain proper food safety and hygiene standards</li>
              <li>Fulfill orders in a timely manner</li>
              <li>Handle customer complaints professionally</li>
              <li>Comply with all applicable laws and regulations</li>
              <li>Pay all fees and charges in a timely manner</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Customer Responsibilities</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">When using our services, customers agree to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
              <li>Provide accurate delivery information</li>
              <li>Pay for orders in full at the time of purchase</li>
              <li>Treat restaurant staff and delivery personnel with respect</li>
              <li>Report any issues or concerns promptly</li>
              <li>Not misuse our AI chatbot or other features</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">5. Payment Terms</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Restaurant subscription fees are billed monthly or annually as agreed upon. Payment is due upon receipt of invoice. 
              Late payments may result in service suspension or termination.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              All prices are subject to change with 30 days' notice. Refunds are provided according to our refund policy.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              OrdersLift retains all rights to our software, technology, and intellectual property. Restaurants retain rights to their 
              brand, menu, and content. You grant us a license to use your content for service provision and improvement.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">7. Data and Privacy</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Your data is protected according to our Privacy Policy. We use data to provide services, improve our AI, and generate 
              insights. You retain ownership of your customer data and can export it at any time.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">8. Service Availability</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              We strive for 99.9% uptime but cannot guarantee uninterrupted service. We are not liable for service interruptions 
              due to maintenance, technical issues, or circumstances beyond our control.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">9. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              OrdersLift's liability is limited to the amount paid for services in the 12 months preceding any claim. We are not 
              liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">10. Indemnification</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              You agree to indemnify and hold harmless OrdersLift from any claims arising from your use of our services, violation 
              of these terms, or infringement of third-party rights.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">11. Termination</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Either party may terminate services with 30 days' written notice. We may terminate immediately for:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
              <li>Violation of these terms</li>
              <li>Non-payment of fees</li>
              <li>Illegal or fraudulent activity</li>
              <li>Material breach of agreement</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">12. Dispute Resolution</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Disputes will be resolved through good faith negotiation. If unresolved, disputes will be settled through binding 
              arbitration in accordance with applicable law.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">13. Governing Law</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              These terms are governed by the laws of the jurisdiction where OrdersLift is incorporated. Any legal action must 
              be brought in the appropriate courts of that jurisdiction.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">14. Changes to Terms</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              We may update these terms from time to time. Material changes will be communicated via email or website notice. 
              Continued use of services constitutes acceptance of updated terms.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">15. Contact Information</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              For questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us:
            </p>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mt-4">
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                <strong>Email:</strong> restaurantorderlift@gmail.com<br>
                <strong>Phone:</strong> (+91) 63939 74340
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer client:load />
</Layout> 